steel flower ( hangul : 스틸 플라워 ; rr : seutil peulrawo ) is a 2015 south korean film starring jeong ha-dam .   written and directed by park suk-young , it depicts the story of a young homeless girl struggling to make a living in busan .   it made its world premiere at the 20th busan international film festival in 2015 .   since then , it has won numerous awards .